        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 5.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 21 18.75V16.5M16.5 12 12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3"></path></svg>
        Centro de Descargas
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-heading font-bold text-cream-50 mb-3">
        Descarga Flujo TV para tu Dispositivo
      </h2>
      <p class="text-cream-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
